Game : PowerStone
Origin : USA - NTSC
Released : June 28th, 2000

Release Notes

Here's another A-quality game to add to your Dreamcast collection. 

Game Info:
~~~~~~~~~~
A new revolution begins. Power Stone kicks off Capcom's lineup on the Sega Dreamcast with the most breathtaking graphics ever seen in a fighting game.

Fully interactive, 3D worlds allow players to interact with the 
environment like never before. Swing off a light post, run up walls
and pick up items like tables and barrels in swashbuckling battles 
with opponents. 

Plus, collect three power stones and your character transforms into a raging super being, executing deadly power fusion moves.

A full review can also be found at:
http://dreamcast.ign.com/reviews/10637.html
